name: mega_arith_variadic_mul_if_operands
section: codegen-arith-variadic
args: p:Bool a:Int b:Int c:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Variadic multiplication must see branch-selected operands and remain commutative around them.
law: (= (* (if {p} {a} {b}) (if {p} {b} {a}) {c}) (* {a} {b} {c}))
